&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.open-std.org/jtc1/sc22/wg21/docs/papers/2007/n2246.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;N2246 2 of the least crazy ideas for the standard library in C++0x&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
